OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA dry and bright start,
OL,6,Fbefore increasing cloud and outbreaks
OL,7,Fof rain, locally heavy, spreads east
OL,8,Facross all parts during the afternoon.
OL,9,FWindy, gusty on coasts and hills.
OL,10,FFeeling humid.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FVariable
OL,13,Fcloud and brighter spells, with a few
OL,14,Fscattered showers Friday, these easing
OL,15,Flater. Breezy. Dry with sunny spells
OL,16,Fon Saturday and Sunday. Feeling much
OL,17,Fwarmer, with light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
